                                                <h3>Information Command <span>
                                                        <tooltip>(click to expand)</tooltip>
                                                    </span></h3>
                                                <ul>
                                                    <li>
                                                        <strong>Description:</strong><br>
                                                        A command which will directly mention a specific user with some
                                                        useful information, such as how to link their socials to their
                                                        Discord profile or how the XP/rank system works
                                                        <br><br>
                                                        <strong>Usage:</strong><br>
                                                        <code>/info [topic] [username]</code>

                                                        <br><br>

                                                        Where <code>topic</code> is the information you are
                                                        referencing<br>
                                                        Where <code>username</code> is the user you are directing the
                                                        information at
                                                    </li>
                                                </ul>
                                            </li>

                                            <li>
                                                <h3>Rule Command <span>
                                                        <tooltip>(click to expand)</tooltip>
                                                    </span></h3>
                                                <ul>
                                                    <li>
                                                        <strong>Description:</strong><br>
                                                        A command which will directly mention a specific user with a
                                                        specific rule. The rule number correlates to the order in which
                                                        they appear in the <channel>#rules</channel> channel
                                                        <br><br>
                                                        <strong>Usage:</strong><br>
